<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lab Results Ready</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fa709a 0%, #fee140 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .results-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #fa709a;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: #fa709a;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ”¬ Lab Results Available</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= patientName %>,</p>
        <p>Your lab test results from <strong>
                <%= clinicName %>
            </strong> are now ready to view.</p>

        <div class="results-card">
            <h3>Test Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Test Type:</strong>
                <%= testType %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Clinic:</strong>
                <%= clinicName %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #28a745; font-weight: bold;">âœ“ Completed</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            <strong>ðŸ“± Access Your Results:</strong>
            <p>Log in to your patient portal to view and download your complete lab results.</p>
        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="<%= portalUrl %>" class="button">View Results</a>
        </center>

        <p><strong>Note:</strong> If you have any questions about your results, please contact your doctor or the
            clinic.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 <%= clinicName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>For medical emergencies, please call emergency services immediately.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>